Package com.authlete.cbor

Class CBORDefaultDecoderOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.cbor.CBORDecoderOptions
      • com.authlete.cbor.CBORDefaultDecoderOptions
  • public class CBORDefaultDecoderOptions
extends CBORDecoderOptions
    The default options for the CBOR decoder (CBORDecoder).

    The following tag processors are registered.

    tag number tag processor description
    2 CPBignum RFC 8949, 3.4.3. Bignums
    3 CPBignum RFC 8949, 3.4.3. Bignums
    16 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 5.2. Single Recipient Encrypted (COSE_Encrypt0)
    17 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 6.2. MACed Messages with Implicit Key (COSE_Mac0)
    18 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 4.2. Signing with One Signer (COSE_Sign1)
    61 CWTTagProcessor RFC 8392, 6. CWT CBOR Tag
    96 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 5.1. Enveloped COSE Structure (COSE_Encrypt)
    97 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 6.1. MACed Message with Recipients (COSE_Mac)
    98 COSEMessageTagProcessor RFC 9052, 4.1. Signing with One or More Signers (COSE_Sign)
